then (( dist (x1,p2) ) <= ( ( dist (x1,p1) ) + ( dist (p1,p2) ) ) & ( dist (x2,p2) ) <= ( dist (x1,p2) )) by A2,A3,A7,CKB26:1,METRIC_1:4;
