( ( dist p1 ) . x1 ) = ( dist (x1,p1) ) by CKB20:def 1;
then (( dist (x2,p1) ) <= ( ( dist (x2,p2) ) + ( dist (p2,p1) ) ) & ( dist (x1,p1) ) <= ( dist (x2,p1) )) by A2,A4,A6,CKB26:1,METRIC_1:4;
then ( dist (x1,p1) ) <= ( ( dist (x2,p2) ) + ( dist (p1,p2) ) ) by XXREAL_0:2;
